PROFOUND AS YOU LIKE ! I AM BY NO MEANS OLD SAID THE FIR TREE ! WE ARE TO HEAR CHRIST WHO HAS BEEN APPOINTED BY THE FATHER AS OUR DIVINE TEACHER ! THERE'S MANY A ONE CONSIDERABLY OLDER THAN I AM ! AT THE SAME TIME PAUL CONFIRMS OUR CREED THAT CHRIST IS VERY GOD ! THEY WERE SO EXTREMELY CURIOUS ! THAT CHRIST IS VERY GOD IS APPARENT IN THAT PAUL ASCRIBES TO HIM DIVINE POWERS EQUALLY WITH THE FATHER AS FOR INSTANCE THE POWER TO DISPENSE GRACE AND PEACE ! I KNOW NO SUCH PLACE SAID THE TREE ! TO BESTOW PEACE AND GRACE LIES IN THE PROVINCE OF GOD WHO ALONE CAN CREATE THESE BLESSINGS THE ANGELS CANNOT ! AND THEN HE TOLD ALL ABOUT HIS YOUTH AND THE LITTLE MICE HAD NEVER HEARD THE LIKE BEFORE AND THEY LISTENED AND SAID ! OTHERWISE PAUL SHOULD HAVE WRITTEN GRACE FROM GOD THE FATHER AND PEACE FROM OUR LORD JESUS CHRIST ! SAID THE FIR TREE THINKING OVER WHAT HE HAD HIMSELF RELATED ! THE ARIANS TOOK CHRIST FOR A NOBLE AND PERFECT CREATURE SUPERIOR EVEN TO THE ANGELS BECAUSE BY HIM GOD CREATED HEAVEN AND EARTH ! YES IN REALITY THOSE WERE HAPPY TIMES ! MOHAMMED ALSO SPEAKS HIGHLY OF CHRIST ! WHO IS HUMPY DUMPY ASKED THE MICE ! PAUL STICKS TO HIS THEME ! ONLY THAT ONE ANSWERED THE TREE ! HE NEVER LOSES SIGHT OF THE PURPOSE OF HIS EPISTLE ! IT IS A VERY STUPID STORY ! NOT GOLD OR SILVER OR PASCHAL LAMBS OR AN ANGEL BUT HIMSELF WHAT FOR ! DON'T YOU KNOW ONE ABOUT BACON AND TALLOW CANDLES CAN'T YOU TELL ANY LARDER STORIES ! NOT FOR A CROWN OR A KINGDOM OR OUR GOODNESS BUT FOR OUR SINS ! NO SAID THE TREE ! UNDERSCORE THESE WORDS FOR THEY ARE FULL OF COMFORT FOR SORE CONSCIENCES ! THEN GOOD BYE SAID THE RATS AND THEY WENT HOME ! HOW MAY WE OBTAIN REMISSION OF OUR SINS ! AT LAST THE LITTLE MICE STAYED AWAY ALSO AND THE TREE SIGHED AFTER ALL IT WAS VERY PLEASANT WHEN THE SLEEK LITTLE MICE SAT ROUND ME AND LISTENED TO WHAT I TOLD THEM ! PAUL ANSWERS THE MAN WHO IS NAMED JESUS CHRIST AND THE SON OF GOD GAVE HIMSELF FOR OUR SINS ! NOW THAT TOO IS OVER ! SINCE CHRIST WAS GIVEN FOR OUR SINS IT STANDS TO REASON THAT THEY CANNOT BE PUT AWAY BY OUR OWN EFFORTS ! WHY ONE MORNING THERE CAME A QUANTITY OF PEOPLE AND SET TO WORK IN THE LOFT ! THIS SENTENCE ALSO DEFINES OUR SINS AS GREAT SO GREAT IN FACT THAT THE WHOLE WORLD COULD NOT MAKE AMENDS FOR A SINGLE SIN ! THE TRUNKS WERE MOVED THE TREE WAS PULLED OUT AND THROWN RATHER HARD IT IS TRUE DOWN ON THE FLOOR BUT A MAN DREW HIM TOWARDS THE STAIRS WHERE THE DAYLIGHT SHONE ! THE GREATNESS OF THE RANSOM CHRIST THE SON OF GOD INDICATES THIS ! BUT IT WAS NOT THE FIR TREE THAT THEY MEANT ! THE VICIOUS CHARACTER OF SIN IS BROUGHT OUT BY THE WORDS WHO GAVE HIMSELF FOR OUR SINS ! IT WAS IN A CORNER THAT HE LAY AMONG WEEDS AND NETTLES ! BUT WE ARE CARELESS WE MAKE LIGHT OF SIN ! THE GOLDEN STAR OF TINSEL WAS STILL ON THE TOP OF THE TREE AND GLITTERED IN THE SUNSHINE ! WE THINK THAT BY SOME LITTLE WORK OR MERIT WE CAN DISMISS SIN ! IN THE COURT YARD SOME OF THE MERRY CHILDREN WERE PLAYING WHO HAD DANCED AT CHRISTMAS ROUND THE FIR TREE AND WERE SO GLAD AT THE SIGHT OF HIM ! THIS PASSAGE THEN BEARS OUT THE FACT THAT ALL MEN ARE SOLD UNDER SIN ! AND THE GARDENER'S BOY CHOPPED THE TREE INTO SMALL PIECES THERE WAS A WHOLE HEAP LYING THERE ! THIS ATTITUDE SPRINGS FROM A FALSE CONCEPTION OF SIN THE CONCEPTION THAT SIN IS A SMALL MATTER EASILY TAKEN CARE OF BY GOOD WORKS THAT WE MUST PRESENT OURSELVES UNTO GOD WITH A GOOD CONSCIENCE THAT WE MUST FEEL NO SIN BEFORE WE MAY FEEL THAT CHRIST WAS GIVEN FOR OUR SINS ! THE WOOD FLAMED UP SPLENDIDLY UNDER THE LARGE BREWING COPPER AND IT SIGHED SO DEEPLY ! THIS ATTITUDE IS UNIVERSAL AND PARTICULARLY DEVELOPED IN THOSE WHO CONSIDER THEMSELVES BETTER THAN OTHERS ! HOWEVER THAT WAS OVER NOW THE TREE GONE THE STORY AT AN END ! BUT THE REAL SIGNIFICANCE AND COMFORT OF THE WORDS FOR OUR SINS IS LOST UPON THEM !
